  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>All meals are served in the hotel's beautiful restaurant. A rich buffet breakfast with hot and cold options are on offer to start your day as well as organic choices.</p>
<p>A free daily tea time buffet is served between 4pm and 5.30pm with both sweet and savoury items to enjoy.</p>
<p>The five-course gourmet dinners are authentic regional dishes made with locally-grown ingredients, including produce grown on their own farm. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
