  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Ladina Double Rooms</strong> sleep two people and are around 28m². Rooms come with a bath or shower and have recently been renovated in a traditional mountain style.</p>
<p><strong>Piz La Ila Double</strong> <strong>Rooms</strong> sleep up to four people (extra bed is a double sofa bed) and are around 45m². They have a walk-in shower in the bathroom.</p>
<p><strong>Natural Loft Suites</strong> sleep up to four people (extra bed is a double sofa bed) and are around 100m². These impressive suites have tea &amp; coffee making facilities, fireplace, bath or shower and a Finnish sauna.</p>
